    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find cats living in the city and befriend them with canned food!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is about exploring one city and befriending cats; invite as many cats as you can to a festival day that will be held in five days. The city is dotted with cat-shaped Jizo statues, which you can talk to for hints on how to explore. Stickers are also hidden throughout the city, and finding them is part of the fun. Use the manholes to instantly move (fast travel) and explore every corner of the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[About the controls]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game can be played with mouse and keyboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >XBOX360 controller can be used for Windows only.</p>",
